reviewText: This one is kinda fun if you like disaster movies.  I hope people really aren't as stupid as some of the characters in this film.  You get out of your truck because it quit running.  You see a tornado coming towards you.  And you get back in your truck and try starting it again?  No go, then take off running down the road still directly in its path.  I guess that speaks to the writing and not the acting.  Still, I liked this movie.  I continue to search for another first rate movie like Night of the Twisters.  That one is A+
Title: F6 Twister

reviewText: I bought this because I like Victoria Pratt. It was an okay movie, but worth seeing to see her. She's transitioned well from the hot/buff period of her career to a really hot middle-aged woman.
Title: F6 Twister

reviewText: I just finished watching the Movie for the 3rd time. I enjoyed the Flick. It was kind of slow and lame in a few spots, But to me the real story stands out. I have been thru a few Tornadoes in my day and I take the warnings seriously. Living in Nebraska, Its not Texas but we have our share of the finger  of God. I have seen people that do not pay attention and that scarces me. I am not a person that really agrees with Global Warming, But I would definately watch this movie again.
Title: F6 Twister
